Missions.Title: Countermeasures
Missions.Description: Fighting the robots makes no sense. Focus on obtaining data drives your coworkers left at their workplace. At least one of them probably contains a virus that can shut down the bots.

Objectives.Description: Can't hurt to have the bot blueprints...

Missions.Title: Strange noises
Missions.Description: The software doesn't disable the robots. Instead they disappear, as well as your coworkers. You hear a strange noise from the basement...

Missions.Title: Enter the portal
Missions.Description: As it seems, you have opened a portal from hell in the server room. Since you're not willing to leave it open, you grab some guns and jump into it...

Missions.Title: The dimension linker
Missions.Description: Turns out that those demons were planning an invasion, using the so called dimension linker. Better steal the linker from them.

Missions.Title: There is always that one guy.
Missions.Description: Out of the sudden, some kind of demon overlord grabs the device. Get it back!

Objectives.Description: Get the device from its cold, dead hands.

Missions.Title: Strange noises
Missions.Description: The portal is closed, the device is smashed, everything seems fine. Suddenly, bright schemes appear, shouting "Nothing shall leave hell alive!"
